query:
INSERT INTO project (
                    id,
                    name,
                    owner,
                    status,
                    sell_price,
                    orderer,
                    note,
                    --structure_group_id,
                    project_group_id,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4::PROJECT_STATUS, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9, $10)
                ON CONFLICT (id)
                DO UPDATE SET
                    name        = EXCLUDED.name,
                    status      = EXCLUDED.status,
                    sell_price  = EXCLUDED.sell_price,
                    orderer     = EXCLUDED.orderer,
                    note        = EXCLUDED.note,
                    updated_at  = EXCLUDED.updated_at
